spec_data.Name: perl-DateTime-Format-W3CDTF
spec_data.Description:
This module understands the W3CDTF date/time format, an ISO 8601 profile,
defined at http://www.w3.org/TR/NOTE-datetime. This format as the native
date format of RSS 1.0.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:56:48 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parse and format W3CDTF datetime strings
